Egypt has been authorized to purchaseabout 200,000 tonnes of U.S. wheat under an existing PL-480agreement, the U.S. Agriculture Department said.    It may buy the wheat, valued at 22.0 mln dlrs, betweenApril 15 and August 31, 1987, and ship it from U.S. ports bySeptember 30, the department said. Reuter&#3;